author: Huawei
description:
Technological innovation is powering South Africa's digital future. Broadband Infraco (BBI) professionals share how the company is building a reliable backbone network with #Huawei's 800G and all-optical technologies. 
 
See how BBI's partnership with Huawei boosts economic growth by engaging SMEs and creating jobs. Together, they're helping SA Connect achieve its 2030 network goals by delivering high-quality broadband to remote communities. Watch to see how collaboration fuels progress and connectivity, and learn more about South Africa's 800G intelligent optical backbone network here: https://bit.ly/4iODW8r #GreenIntelligentOptiX #OXC #800GBackbone
title: BBI Trusts Huawei Tech to Bridge South Africa's Digital Divide

author: Huawei
description:
Can South Africa address its digital divide and achieve 100% broadband connectivity by 2030? That's the goal Broadband Infraco (BBI) and #Huawei are working toward. Together, they're building South Africa's 800G intelligent optical backbone network, advancing SA Connect's 2030 vision and driving digital progress in healthcare, education, government, and more.
 
BBI has already connected 2 million rural homes and more than 13,000 public Wi-Fi hotspots. Watch to discover how their collaboration with Huawei is empowering South Africa with digital connectivity: https://bit.ly/48HWdzM #GreenIntelligentOptiX #OXC #800GBackbone
title: South Africa's Digital Highway for All: Powered by BBI and Huawei
